{"tid":1507561,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"陳雲：不是時代革命，是香港革命","createTime":"2019-08-26T08:04:27.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-26T16:04:02.000Z","uid":292536,"like":7,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"8c6247cc58b5b4fc8f38c6ee6824e6c812ebac5e","tid":1507561,"uid":292536,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-26T08:04:27.000Z","msg":"陳雲：昨晚，打響了香港革命的第一槍，這是敵方意外地為我們響起的集結號，令我們無比的惶恐與欣慰。敵方終於用槍聲肯定，我們是認真的。<br />\n<br />\n今年是香港的成年禮。初生的華英共和國，遇上老大的蘇維埃王朝，注定要大打一場，之後各行各路。你有你鎖國愚昧，我有我開放聰穎。<br />\n<br />\n所謂反對逃犯引渡條例修訂，只是香港建國戰役的藉口，我們無心保護在港的財閥富豪的家財性命，財閥富豪也無心保護我們的赤裸身軀，彼此漠不關心。我們只是慶幸在這個無事發生的沉悶世界，找到大打一場的浪漫藉口。我們慷慨地將憲政民主的香港，施捨給漠不關心的富豪財閥，一群躲在在高樓廣宅的政治乞丐。<br />\n<br />\n不是時代革命，是香港革命。不要遮遮掩掩，要夠膽講出來。我們從未統治過香港，故此不是光復香港，而是解放香港。敵方都為我們開了槍火，不要遮遮掩掩，要夠膽講出來。<br />\n<br />\n解放殖民，香港革命。打完了，香港成人長進，立於強國之林。美國走進來，世界捲入來，做我們建國鬥爭的見證。"},{"pid":"4536048ce934311a25ee31dbef57c24b39a83fa7","tid":1507561,"uid":33930,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-26T08:04:40.000Z","msg":"唔好意思借個post宣傳一下<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/4GJMrJb.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F4GJMrJb.jpg&h=cb7c9807&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n901 和你塞  13:00 見   <a href=\"http://t.me/stuckwithyou\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fstuckwithyou&d=TNp%2FFCzVUvAW3I%2FC9AhTY2o8q5%2FbnpuKyKF%2Fs7IAglk%3D&h=0e4f3917\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">t.me/stuckwithyou</a>"},{"pid":"b77d30ad05580e8b4aff430357a0528357c8ca9d","tid":1507561,"uid":292536,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-26T08:07:02.000Z","msg":"p"},{"pid":"f1d23aace15df7529a3689e3010d1d7d06f2fea0","tid":1507561,"uid":149630,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-26T08:17:46.000Z","msg":"［解放殖民，香港革命］昨晚，打響了香港革命的第一槍<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1507581\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1507581</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"242ecaad6dc366bd7b94232a297e18e781044802","tid":1507561,"uid":292536,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-26T08:54:05.000Z","msg":"自推"},{"pid":"a0a43cbfab90af353dee33e591c54e2fb27bab9d","tid":1507561,"uid":149630,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-26T10:14:53.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"c5021b68422cde304f5540ecf0566946a9f75b18","tid":1507561,"uid":251732,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-26T11:05:09.000Z","msg":"始終都要將呢個反送中運動，轉化為香港解放革命"},{"pid":"550547afbfb4ae28f7b003aa34571b7ea9687972","tid":1507561,"uid":300554,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-26T14:19:49.000Z","msg":"【入嚟填呀！】升級罷工，全民自決。網民發起問卷調查！<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1508197\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1508197</a><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/KpD40fE.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FKpD40fE.jpg&h=6cea06ce&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/5dCmh2k.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F5dCmh2k.jpg&h=274a80cb&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"597d9b6bf516f94d1fe85981a43f0ba947ad515a","tid":1507561,"uid":46804,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-26T16:04:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />支持林鄭"}]}